# ESLint & Formatting Guide

## Linting
- Use ESLint with the recommended and TypeScript plugins.
- Fix all lint errors before commit.

## Formatting
- Use Prettier for code formatting; auto-format on save.
- Maintain consistent indentation (2 spaces).

## Import Order
- Use ESLint plugin for import sorting.

## Commit Hooks
- Use pre-commit hooks to run lint and format checks.
